    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains rigid with refreshed bushings and a factory-spec suspension setup that retains its legendary turn-in response. Cosmetically honest with a driver-focused cockpit, this vehicle is optimized for the purist who values mechanical transparency and high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
